M221 S100 ;Set the flow rate to 100%
M104 S180      ;  Set the extruder to an initial temperature of 180 just to get the hot end heated
M140 S{bed_temperature_initial_layer_single}       ;  start the bed heading
G90
CG28
Custom_Print_Start BED_TEMP=[bed_temperature_initial_layer_single] EXTRUDER_TEMP=[nozzle_temperature_initial_layer] BED_MESH=adaptive   TIMER=30 X_START=5 Y_START=13 X_END=80 Y_END=13 FIRST_LAYER=+0.00 Sensor=True
